produced & engineered by Norbert Ol├íh
recorded in Budapest ┬Ě mixed with machines ┬Ě mastered by hand
no cookies ┬Ě no trackers ┬Ě no skill bars

you're reading the source. correct instinct. stdin is open: press ~
